{"tid":1007293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應召妹無言！客點2小時全套服務　竟要她幫忙搬家","createTime":"2019-02-03T16:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T15:17:41.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1002,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"08d86795115a5998f3c06b6a3b5e84315cecf64b","tid":1007293,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190203/640_75b400817ec93ad57bbc9bc38e8a2ee9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190203%2F640_75b400817ec93ad57bbc9bc38e8a2ee9.jpg&h=43d8a985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應召妹到客人家準備服務時，沒想到客人根本不想啪啪啪，只是把她叫來幫忙搬家。<br />\n<br />\n日本女網友「みゆな」在《推特》發文抱怨，問在做風俗業的同行小姐們，「除了我以外，有人被客人點了2小時服務叫到家裡，然後幫忙搬家的經驗嗎？」還說幸好有小貨車可以運送。<br />\n<br />\n同行的女網友紛紛述說自己的經驗「我有遇過點3小時服務然後要幫忙搬家的，結束後還剩一些時間還打掃跟吃飯」、「我也有遇過要打掃、洗碗、洗床單的」、「雖然沒有遇過要幫家的，不過有遇過腰受傷不能動，要我幫忙餵飯吃的」，有網友說明，找應召妹搬家其實很划算，找搬家公司根本貴翻了。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"68adf608ad7bdeb3ac9dae962d3e21e3e1581c20","tid":1007293,"uid":77355,"like":167,"dislike":4,"score":163,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7e5876c422c47dce9075d7dfc4a827703ceb11","tid":1007293,"uid":511,"like":640,"dislike":4,"score":636,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"喺床比人屌仲&quot;他條&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd0e0be2869d6f7dfc028658616f8e2d081ea79","tid":1007293,"uid":210525,"like":234,"dislike":3,"score":231,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:09:47.000Z","msg":"又係一條出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f82658ad3bf1684eea99e1f26ce538d31a80f5","tid":1007293,"uid":39608,"like":283,"dislike":4,"score":279,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:10:43.000Z","m